    <lb n="25"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ω, ἐὰν δὲ ᾖ</supplied> βουλευτή<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear>, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ημεύσει ὑποβάλλω. διὸ παρεγγυῶ τοῖς 

